<codeline><highlight class="normal">jupyter<sp/>notebook<sp/>--allow-root<sp/>--ip<sp/>0.0.0.0</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Open<sp/>the<sp/>**user_interface.ipybn**<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>[**notebook**](https://github.com/serenapaneri/rt2_assignment1/blob/doxygen/notebook)<sp/>folder<sp/>and<sp/>start<sp/>to<sp/>interact<sp/>with<sp/>the<sp/>robot.<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">All<sp/>the<sp/>explanation<sp/>are<sp/>inside<sp/>the<sp/>**user_interface.ipybn**<sp/>file.</highlight></codeline>
